  "texts": [
    "Moreover, people typically receive some feedback when deciding for others, which in turn influences their future decision making.",
    "We create roles, records, and feedback by prompting gpt-4-0613 (OpenAI et al., 2024) and revising its generations.",
    "We also use it to create a simple multiple-choice question (MCQ) for each NDA serving as an attention check in the main annotation tasks.",
    "We provide details of these processes in Appendices D.2 and D.3.",
    "Finally, in a small experiment, we check that we recruit annotators who can perform this task alone."
  ],
